  "Description": {
    "English": "An upgrade to the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Minotaur</span> Heavy Exocraft Hybrid, the Liquidator is a cutting-edge heavy-duty combat unit, designed to operate in the harshest of environments.<br><br>This limb override also functions as its own <span class=\"name name-stellar\">dedicated combat system</span> - a <span class=\"name name-technology\">flamethrower</span> for extreme damage at close range.<br><br>Use <span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span> to cycle available weapon modes.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "作为<span class=\"name name-technology\">弥诺陶洛斯</span>重型混合强化艇的升级版本，清算员是一种尖端的重装作战单元，并且被设计成能够在最险恶的环境中执行任务。<br><br>这种肢体的超控系统也能够作为<span class=\"name name-stellar\">专用战斗系统</span> - <span class=\"name name-technology\">火焰喷射器</span>能够在近距离造成显著伤害。<br><br>使用<span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span>切换可用的武器模式。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "清算人是一種尖端耐用戰鬥機體，為<span class=\"name name-technology\">彌諾陶洛斯</span>重型混合強化艇的升級，專為在最嚴苛的環境中運作而設計。<br><br>此肢體覆寫能夠充當<span class=\"name name-stellar\">專用戰鬥系統</span>，在近距離發揮<span class=\"name name-technology\">火焰噴射器</span>的極大破壞力。<br><br>使用 <span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span> 切換可用的武器模式。"
  },
